@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_abovgf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (v1 / ((v1 + 0.62 * tmp + 0.54) / v0))
    v2 = wp.abs(0.03)
    v0 = wp.abs((tmp / 0.57))
    tmp = wp.cos(v2)
    v0 = (0.40 + (wp.abs(v0 + 0.80) * v2))
    tmp = (0.98 / v2)
    data[tid] = v0
